>不知道是不是我火星了，反正感觉挺惊喜，看看有没有人还不知道</p>\n<p>心血来潮试试，竟然成功了</p>\n<p>sudo apt install chromium-browser</p>\n<p>chromium</p>\n<p>牛逼！</p>\n<p>这是怎么实现的呢？</p>\n","last_modified":1703127200,"replies":15,"id":1002178},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1630643991","name":"iphone","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1630643991","title":"iPhone","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","topics":11033,"footer":"这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。","header":"Say hello to the future.","title_alternative":"iPhone","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","stars":3293,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":8,"parent_node_name":"apple"},"member":{"id":575309,"username":"pclsm","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/pclsm","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a4a3/f62d/575309_mini.png?m=1701878881","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a4a3/f62d/575309_normal.png?m=1701878881","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a4a3/f62d/575309_large.png?m=1701878881","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a4a3/f62d/575309_xlarge.png?m=1701878881","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a4a3/f62d/575309_xlarge.png?m=1701878881","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a4a3/f62d/575309_xlarge.png?m=1701878881","created":1647246658,"last_modified":1701878881},"last_reply_by":"zjuster","last_touched":1703125346,"title":"iphone15 pro 更新到 17.2.1 后电信卡无服务","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1002136","created":1703119970,"deleted":0,"content":"iPhone 15 pro ，移动电信双卡，没有升级以前移动信号稍好，电信信号也勉强能接受。\r\n\r\n昨天更新到 17.2.1 后，移动信号变好，平时地铁上信号较弱，打开网站都卡顿的地段可以流畅的刷视频了。\r\n\r\n电信卡直接显示无服务，但是设置里还是可以读取到手机号。开始以为卡坏了，换到小米 13 ，正常联网打电话。\r\n\r\n将另外一张电话卡，也是电信的，插入 iPhone 15 pro 后正常联网打电话。\r\n\r\n在 iPhone 上更换卡槽，单卡双卡都试过，始终显示无服务。\r\n\r\n准备到营业厅换卡试试。\r\n\r\n各位有遇到过类似问题吗？","content_rendered":"<p>iPhone 15 pro ，移动电信双卡，没有升级以前移动信号稍好，电信信号也勉强能接受。</p>\n<p>昨天更新到 17.2.1 后，移动信号变好，平时地铁上信号较弱，打开网站都卡顿的地段可以流畅的刷视频了。</p>\n<p>电信卡直接显示无服务，但是设置里还是可以读取到手机号。开始以为卡坏了，换到小米 13 ，正常联网打电话。</p>\n<p>将另外一张电话卡，也是电信的，插入 iPhone 15 pro 后正常联网打电话。</p>\n<p>在 iPhone 上更换卡槽，单卡双卡都试过，始终显示无服务。</p>\n<p>准备到营业厅换卡试试。</p>\n<p>各位有遇到过类似问题吗？</p>\n","last_modified":1703119970,"replies":15,"id":1002136},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc22/1309/181_large.png?m=1608240651","name":"travel","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc22/1309/181_normal.png?m=1608240651","title":"旅行","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/travel","topics":947,"footer":"","header":"你会把上大学的学费用来环游世界么？","title_alternative":"Travel","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc22/1309/181_mini.png?m=1608240651","stars":1000,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":181,"parent_node_name":"life"},"member":{"id":328194,"username":"37Y37","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/37Y37","website":"https://blog.ops-coffee.cn","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e80130f0e891c74c0757e084e2854259?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e80130f0e891c74c0757e084e2854259?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e80130f0e891c74c0757e084e2854259?s=73&d=retro","created":1531206003,"last_modified":1643689570},"last_reply_by":"37Y37","last_touched":1703125762,"title":"2023 年房车使用及旅行总结","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1002134","created":1703118856,"deleted":0,"content":"年初站内有小伙伴问今年的目标是什么，我写下了每月至少一次的旅行，一年时间过的真快，目标已经完成，回顾一下简单做个总结\r\n\r\n这一年自驾 2 万多公里，足迹 3 省 11 市，12 个月写下了 13 篇游记...\r\n\r\nhttps://blog.ops-coffee.cn/r/2023-rv-travel-camping-and-vanlife","content_rendered":"<p>年初站内有小伙伴问今年的目标是什么，我写下了每月至少一次的旅行，一年时间过的真快，目标已经完成，回顾一下简单做个总结</p>\n<p>这一年自驾 2 万多公里，足迹 3 省 11 市，12 个月写下了 13 篇游记...</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.ops-coffee.cn/r/2023-rv-travel-camping-and-vanlife\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://blog.ops-coffee.cn/r/2023-rv-travel-camping-and-vanlife</a></p>\n","last_modified":1703118856,"replies":13,"id":1002134},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":213466,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":4058,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":654059,"username":"kemo","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/kemo","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a3138872d871d2b066bccec08b743a72?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a3138872d871d2b066bccec08b743a72?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a3138872d871d2b066bccec08b743a72?s=73&d=retro","created":1696920375,"last_modified":1702277581},"last_reply_by":"JasonFW","last_touched":1703130880,"title":"被兴业消费金融起诉了，快开庭了怎么办","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1002176","created":1703126864,"deleted":0,"content":"我是 2020 年 11 月份左右通过中介向兴业消费金融贷款 12 万元，当时支付中介费 10%，就是 1.2 万(不支付，兴业消费贷款客户经理不签，为什么这样借钱？反正一个年轻人走错了路，这帖子里不谈了)，截止 2022 年 10 月份，总计利息和本金还了 9 万块，因为上海口罩和失业、负债的原因，无奈逾期。然后今年开始打工，这个月收到了兴业消费金融的起诉信息，要求我偿还剩余本金和利息总计 9 万元，还有律师费 1300 元。\r\n也就是说我用 12 万，一共三年的时间，需要向对方偿还 12000+90000+90000+1300=193,300 元，总计多还 73300 元。\r\n这快开庭了，兴业消费金融调解不同意分期方案，要求一次性偿还本金和诉讼费 7 万块，而我现在一下子又拿不出这么多钱。\r\n我想问下，这种情况我要不要去上海参加开庭呢，如果被判败诉，强制执行的话会将名下所有银行卡都封了吗？\r\n我是不是可以说他们违规放贷呢，因为不仅收了中介费，还有申请时联系我家人说是办理信用卡，实际是消费贷，这种情况我该怎么做呢？\r\n钱肯定是要还的，合法的利息也会还的，超出利息我宁愿被强制也不愿意还，所以现在我该怎么做","content_rendered":"<p>我是 2020 年 11 月份左右通过中介向兴业消费金融贷款 12 万元，当时支付中介费 10%，就是 1.2 万(不支付，兴业消费贷款客户经理不签，为什么这样借钱？反正一个年轻人走错了路，这帖子里不谈了)，截止 2022 年 10 月份，总计利息和本金还了 9 万块，因为上海口罩和失业、负债的原因，无奈逾期。然后今年开始打工，这个月收到了兴业消费金融的起诉信息，要求我偿还剩余本金和利息总计 9 万元，还有律师费 1300 元。\n也就是说我用 12 万，一共三年的时间，需要向对方偿还 12000+90000+90000+1300=193,300 元，总计多还 73300 元。\n这快开庭了，兴业消费金融调解不同意分期方案，要求一次性偿还本金和诉讼费 7 万块，而我现在一下子又拿不出这么多钱。\n我想问下，这种情况我要不要去上海参加开庭呢，如果被判败诉，强制执行的话会将名下所有银行卡都封了吗？\n我是不是可以说他们违规放贷呢，因为不仅收了中介费，还有申请时联系我家人说是办理信用卡，实际是消费贷，这种情况我该怎么做呢？\n钱肯定是要还的，合法的利息也会还的，超出利息我宁愿被强制也不愿意还，所以现在我该怎么做</p>\n","last_modified":1703126864,"replies":12,"id":1002176},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1630643991","name":"iphone","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1630643991","title":"iPhone","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","topics":11033,"footer":"这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。","header":"Say hello to the future.","title_alternative":"iPhone","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","stars":3293,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":8,"parent_node_name":"apple"},"member":{"id":579820,"username":"lmkyl","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/lmkyl","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/70adbfeec4c4319e0ae4f5c686fc7353?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/70adbfeec4c4319e0ae4f5c686fc7353?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/70adbfeec4c4319e0ae4f5c686fc7353?s=73&d=retro","created":1651450152,"last_modified":1651450152},"last_reply_by":"lmkyl","last_touched":1703129065,"title":"中国电信 App 也开始检测游戏加速器了","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1002164","created":1703125233,"deleted":0,"content":"从 10.5.3 升级到了 11.0.0 ，闪退\r\n反馈给 10000 ，答：看下有没有安装 VPN\r\n挂断电话，关掉游戏加速器，正常了\r\n一些国家队的 App 至少提示，电信直接玩闪退，好的，删","content_rendered":"<p>从 10.5.3 升级到了 11.0.0 ，闪退\n反馈给 10000 ，答：看下有没有安装 VPN\n挂断电话，关掉游戏加速器，正常了\n一些国家队的 App 至少提示，电信直接玩闪退，好的，删</p>\n","last_modified":1703125233,"replies":11,"id":1002164},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1701170912","name":"share","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1701170912","title":"分享发现","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","topics":40108,"footer":"","header":"分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。","title_alternative":"Share","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1701170912","stars":5650,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":16,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":5055,"username":"sdjl","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/sdjl","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"贵州安顺","tagline":"接微信小程序整包项目开发（我是企业）","bio":"专注微信小程序开发，使用微信云开发。\r\n\r\n接整包外包，价格比市场价贵一些。","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/be6a/d876/5055_mini.png?m=1677142026","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/be6a/d876/5055_normal.png?m=1677142026","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/be6a/d876/5055_large.png?m=1677142026","created":1294652197,"last_modified":1677142026},"last_reply_by":"kuma42710","last_touched":1703125695,"title":"我发现豆瓣游戏评分的“平台拉高”现象","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1002154","created":1703124286,"deleted":0,"content":"先说结论：游戏上架使用人数越多的平台，评分就会被拉得越高。\r\n\r\n举例说明：若一个游戏登录了 Switch 平台，豆瓣评分是 8 分，假设这个游戏后来登录了手机平台，豆瓣评分会被拉高到 9 分以上。\r\n\r\n我说的游戏评分的高与低是一种主观感受，所以这里说的“拉高”是指一种“游戏评分看起来很高，但是我实际游玩体验并没有评价那么高”的感受。我想强调的是这种感受除了和游戏发售年代（受当年机能限制）有关系外，还和在哪个平台上架有关系。\r\n\r\n我们从“使用人数”这个角度给各个平台排一个序：手机 > PC > Switch > PS > xBox （这个排序不一定正确） 。我的观点是“一个在 PS 上 8 分的游戏，通常比在手游上 9 分的游戏好玩得多（假设两个游戏在同一时期发布）”。\r\n\r\n这个发现有啥用？ 也许没啥用，但我现在看游戏评分的时候，我会看一下这个游戏上架了哪些平台，我会根据上架的平台来修正这个游戏在我心中的评分。","content_rendered":"<p>先说结论：游戏上架使用人数越多的平台，评分就会被拉得越高。</p>\n<p>举例说明：若一个游戏登录了 Switch 平台，豆瓣评分是 8 分，假设这个游戏后来登录了手机平台，豆瓣评分会被拉高到 9 分以上。</p>\n<p>我说的游戏评分的高与低是一种主观感受，所以这里说的“拉高”是指一种“游戏评分看起来很高，但是我实际游玩体验并没有评价那么高”的感受。我想强调的是这种感受除了和游戏发售年代（受当年机能限制）有关系外，还和在哪个平台上架有关系。</p>\n<p>我们从“使用人数”这个角度给各个平台排一个序：手机 &gt; PC &gt; Switch &gt; PS &gt; xBox （这个排序不一定正确） 。我的观点是“一个在 PS 上 8 分的游戏，通常比在手游上 9 分的游戏好玩得多（假设两个游戏在同一时期发布）”。</p>\n<p>这个发现有啥用？ 也许没啥用，但我现在看游戏评分的时候，我会看一下这个游戏上架了哪些平台，我会根据上架的平台来修正这个游戏在我心中的评分。</p>\n","last_modified":1703124286,"replies":11,"id":1002154},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1701170912","name":"share","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1701170912","title":"分享发现","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","topics":40107,"footer":"","header":"分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。","title_alternative":"Share","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1701170912","stars":5650,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":16,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":502736,"username":"Yuesh1","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Yuesh1","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cc50bd5bf29e3a5e06a41a2f8edec3f9?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cc50bd5bf29e3a5e06a41a2f8edec3f9?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cc50bd5bf29e3a5e06a41a2f8edec3f9?s=73&d=retro","created":1596765998,"last_modified":1689306329},"last_reply_by":"sadfQED2","last_touched":1703126430,"title":"年度输入法单词-成都","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1002149","created":1703123211,"deleted":0,"content":"年度输入法单词-成都\r\n年度删除单词-成都\r\n\r\n\r\n打开 ssh ，输入“成都”， 删除“成都”。\r\n\r\n\r\n有感而发","content_rendered":"年度输入法单词-成都<br />年度删除单词-成都<br /><br /><br />打开 ssh ，输入“成都”， 删除“成都”。<br /><br /><br />有感而发","last_modified":1703124957,"replies":11,"id":1002149},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":24552,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2836,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name