avatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1700771269","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":60432,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1700771269","stars":8771,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":145501,"username":"mikaelson","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mikaelson","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3598/81dd/145501_mini.png?m=1692764599","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3598/81dd/145501_normal.png?m=1692764599","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3598/81dd/145501_large.png?m=1692764599","created":1446520299,"last_modified":1692764599},"last_reply_by":"mikaelson","last_touched":1703128274,"title":"clash 可以做到代理失效的情况下只允许访问白名单吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1002168","created":1703125533,"deleted":0,"content":"我目前打算是把，允许访问的白名单写在配置文件里，用 DIRECT 。\r\n其余的都走代理\r\n在 rules 的最后加一句 MATCH,REJECT\r\n\r\n这样是不是可以实现有代理的时候，都可以访问，没代理的时候，只允许访问 DIRECT 这些？其余的全部没网。\r\n - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,DIRECT\r\n - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,google.com,PROXY\r\n - MATCH,REJECT\r\n \r\n 这样可以实现这个需求吗？\r\n \r\n 代理失效的情况下，只有白名单可以访问，其余都不允许。\r\n 代理生效的时候就正常使用。","content_rendered":"我目前打算是把，允许访问的白名单写在配置文件里，用 DIRECT 。<br />其余的都走代理<br />在 rules 的最后加一句 MATCH,REJECT<br /><br />这样是不是可以实现有代理的时候，都可以访问，没代理的时候，只允许访问 DIRECT 这些？其余的全部没网。<br /> - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,DIRECT<br /> - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://google.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">google.com</a>,PROXY<br /> - MATCH,REJECT<br /> <br /> 这样可以实现这个需求吗？<br /> <br /> 代理失效的情况下，只有白名单可以访问，其余都不允许。<br /> 代理生效的时候就正常使用。","last_modified":1703125533,"replies":9,"id":1002168}]